  (lib_symbols)

  (text "HiveSync Gateway Schematic\nRaspberry Pi Zero 2W + ESP32-S3 + CC1101 + BG96 LTE + GPS\n\nPi: Main compute, runs Python gateway software\nESP32-S3: Sub-GHz radio controller + Wi-Fi/BLE\nCC1101: 868 MHz mesh radio on SPI\nBG96: LTE-M fallback modem on UART\nPA1616S: GPS on UART2\nStorage: 32GB eMMC\nPower: 5W solar + 2×18650 Li-Ion" (at 200 200) (uuid text1))
